OL,3,CColour Thursday - People urged to shop
OL,4,Clocally as 'antidote' to Black Friday
OL,6,FIndependent retailers on a town's high
OL,7,Fstreet are coming together to
OL,8,Fencourage people to shop locally, as
OL,9,Fonline retail giants try to tempt
OL,10,Fshoppers with Black Friday deals.
OL,12,FAround 30 shops in Tetbury,
OL,13,FGloucestershire, are staying open late
OL,14,Fon Thursday 28 November to showcase
OL,15,Ftheir products as part of the 'Colour
OL,16,FThursday' event.
