OL,3,CColour Thursday - People urged to shop
OL,4,Clocally as 'antidote' to Black Friday
OL,6,FSamantha Whiteside, shop manager at
OL,7,FHenrietta's House, an independent
OL,8,Fbusiness which sells traditional
OL,9,Fchildren's toys, said the event aims
OL,10,Fto offer an "antidote" to Black Friday.
OL,12,F"Tetbury is full of independent
OL,13,Fbusinesses, and it's a chance for us
OL,14,Fto all come together to showcase what
OL,15,Fa great town it is and how unique we
OL,16,Fall are," she said.
