OL,3,CColour Thursday - People urged to shop
OL,4,Clocally as 'antidote' to Black Friday
OL,6,FMs Whiteside added: "We want to make
OL,7,Fthe high street a great place for
OL,8,Fpeople to come and shop, with a
OL,9,Fdiverse range of retailers that offer
OL,10,Fsomething for everyone.
OL,12,F"In the last 12 months, we have gained
OL,13,Fa lot of new independent businesses,
OL,14,Fand the more shops we have, the more
OL,15,Fpeople come in, so for us, it makes a
OL,16,Fhuge difference."
