OL,3,CColour Thursday - People urged to shop
OL,4,Clocally as 'antidote' to Black Friday
OL,6,FThe event was inspired by 'Colour
OL,7,FFriday', a national campaign launched
OL,8,Fin 2021 which aims to redistribute
OL,9,Fsome of the money spent on Black
OL,10,FFriday to independent retailers.
OL,12,FLocal artist Brian Van Zyl has created
OL,13,Fa special hand-drawn map illustrating
OL,14,Fall the independent retailers taking
OL,15,Fpart in the event.
OL,17,FPatsy Robinson, owner of spa and hair
OL,18,Fsalon Mayfair and Grace, said
OL,19,Findependent businesses play a vital
OL,20,Frole in supporting the town.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
