OL,3,CColour Thursday - People urged to shop
OL,4,Clocally as 'antidote' to Black Friday
OL,6,F"We employ 12 people, which is quite a
OL,7,Flot for a small town. And obviously
OL,8,Fthat means we support 12 people's
OL,9,Flivelihoods," she said.
OL,11,F"Businesses are fragile at the moment
OL,12,Fand if we don't have support from our
OL,13,Flocal community, or even the wider
OL,14,Fcommunity, the businesses won't be
OL,15,Fhere for when they need them."
OL,17,FMs Robinson said that as well as
OL,18,Fopening late, they will be offering
OL,19,Fcomplimentary gift wrapping for
OL,20,Fcustomers to provide a "personal
OL,21,Ftouch."
