OL,6,F"What small businesses can offer, is
OL,7,Findividual service," she said. "We
OL,8,Freally do give a bit more because we
OL,9,Fcare about our customers."
OL,11,FShe added: "We can help tailor things
OL,12,Fto people's budgets, make it look
OL,13,Freally special and go the extra mile."
